* peano.adt describes the abstract data-type

* [ Nat, zero, zero ] is equivalent to:
   %op Nat zero { ...}

* [ Nat, suc, suc(<pred(Nat)>) ] is equivalent to:
   %op Nat suc(pred:Nat) { ...}

*  adt-to-tom --input peano.adt --javagen --name peano --nojar

* jtom Peano1.t
* javac Peano1.java
* java Peano1

